WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.500
45-second guide: CashFlow Tracker. Sign in with Google to open your private workspace.

00:00:05.500 --> 00:00:12.000
Overview summarizes your month and highlights where money is moving.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:19.500
Use Quick Add when you want precise control over every field.

00:00:19.500 --> 00:00:27.000
Smart Input parses plain English with local NLP or Claude AI.

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:33.500
Goals turns your activity into a health score and visible progress.

00:00:33.500 --> 00:00:41.000
Setup controls currency, budget limits, recurring items, and AI behavior.

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:45.000
Your simple routine: log spending, review your overview, tune budgets, grow your goals. Return to Overview and watch your financial picture take shape.
